<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-10384] Shutdown broken when using Spring Boot</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-10384</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Camel doesn&apos;t shutdown properly in a Spring Boot environment. Calling the /shutdown endpoint causes Camel to hang-up after stopping the CamelContext. The reason for this is the count-down latch in the CamelSpringBootApplicationController. The overriden Main class modifies the latch in the Main class itself, not the one in CamelSpringBootApplicationController. As a result, the latch in CamelSpringBootApplicationController is waiting forever preventing a proper shutdown.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-style: solid;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;CamelSpringBootApplicationController .java&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; CamelSpringBootApplicationController(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; ApplicationContext applicationContext, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; CamelContext camelContext) {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.main = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Main() {
             
            ...

            @Override
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;protected&lt;/span&gt; void doStop() &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; Exception {
                LOG.debug(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Controller is shutting down CamelContext&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
                    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;super&lt;/span&gt;.doStop();
                } &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;finally&lt;/span&gt; {
                    &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// Should be CamelSpringBootApplicationController.&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.latch.countDown();
&lt;/span&gt;                    latch.countDown();
                }
            }
        };
    }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
